ces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1a014f90792820bd4ca31b57787ceb99b243767","tid":121104,"uid":59666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T10:16:54.000Z","msg":"我的話最起碼都會plan 3日 你當落山休息一日又好 遊吓屋久島又好"},{"pid":"0974ff248eb1e394afd47ab2d7a5dafb48c4facf","tid":121104,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T14:05:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去過，繩紋衫上山，訓左一晚，白谷雲水峽落。 <br />\n第二日落山，膝頭哥痛撚到行唔倒路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊間小屋訓？"},{"pid":"1038df2433709bf7043c08dee526addf94b98e3d","tid":121104,"uid":50961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T15:37:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去過，繩紋衫上山，訓左一晚，白谷雲水峽落。 <br />\n第二日落山，膝頭哥痛撚到行唔倒路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊間小屋訓？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n原本想去高㙇小屋嘅，但去到覺得間屋好臭同有d陰森，所以臨時轉plan 去新高塚。<br />\n其實要行遠好多，但個段路因為少好多人行，所以沿路見倒幾隻鹿同馬騮。最重要係，新高塚間屋離廁所有一段距，所以屋仔唔會有公廁味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 夜晚好似有小動物出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我覺得屋久島係值得留多幾日嘅，我有租車揸，去環下島，吹下海風係幾正。 如果夾到啱時間仲可以睇海龜屙蛋/海龜仔。"},{"pid":"0f2cf650d8c3dcf70e0ca30a73b968211dc64a23","tid":121104,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-15T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去過，繩紋衫上山，訓左一晚，白谷雲水峽落。 <br />\n第二日落山，膝頭哥痛撚到行唔倒路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊間小屋訓？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n原本想去高㙇小屋嘅，但去到覺得間屋好臭同有d陰森，所以臨時轉plan 去新高塚。<br />\n其實要