.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我覺得屋久島係值得留多幾日嘅，我有租車揸，去環下島，吹下海風係幾正。 如果夾到啱時間仲可以睇海龜屙蛋/海龜仔。</blockquote><br />\n其實邊一邊既登山口有冇咩分別</blockquote><br />\n就巴士時間</blockquote><br />\n即係邊一邊上山都無所謂，可以互通？"},{"pid":"10c5f5f57b3d6fa9ee0ff0da9ddbfba16d4e440b","tid":121104,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 識玩wor poba"},{"pid":"2e81290f1a0f153aa806f2815aa1e9cee6565f8d","tid":121104,"uid":50961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去過，繩紋衫上山，訓左一晚，白谷雲水峽落。 <br />\n第二日落山，膝頭哥痛撚到行唔倒路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊間小屋訓？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n原本想去高㙇小屋嘅，但去到覺得間屋好臭同有d陰森，所以臨時轉plan 去新高塚。<br />\n其實要行遠好多，但個段路因為少好多人行，所以沿路見倒幾隻鹿同馬騮。最重要係，新高塚間屋離廁所有一段距，所以屋仔唔會有公廁味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 夜晚好似有小動物出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我覺得屋久島係值得留多幾日嘅，我有租車揸，去環下島，吹下海風係幾正。 如果夾到啱時間仲可以睇海龜屙蛋/海龜仔。</blockquote><br />\n其實邊一邊既登山口有冇咩分別</blockquote><br />\n就巴士時間</blockquote><br />\n即係邊一邊上山都無所謂，可以互通？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去邊度咪上邊個登山口囉。 <br />\n你打開個map就會睇倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c669a2175d0542759f895c8ec28ffb078da3852c","tid":121104,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去過，繩紋衫上山，訓左一晚，白谷雲水峽落。 <br />\n第二日落山，膝頭哥痛撚到行唔倒路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去邊間小屋訓？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n原本想去高㙇小屋嘅，但去到覺得間屋好臭同有d陰森，所以臨時轉plan 去新高塚。<br />\n其實要行遠好多，但個段路因為少好多人行，所以沿路見倒幾隻鹿同馬騮。最重要係，新高塚間屋離廁所有一段距，所以屋仔唔會有公廁味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 夜晚好似有小動物出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋我覺得屋久島係值得留多幾日嘅，我有租車揸，去環下島，吹下海風係幾正。 如果夾到啱時間仲可以睇海龜屙蛋/海龜仔。</blockquote><br />\n其實邊一邊既登山口有冇咩分別</blockquote><br />\n就巴士時間</blockquote><br />\n即係邊一邊上山都無所謂，可以互通？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n伸手黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你去邊度咪上邊個登山口囉。 <br />\n你打開個map就會睇倒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n網上唔多地圖係縱走，而家問清楚都唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又要屌又要答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a141c16051ad7534200d0814573c154cf5d16f6","tid":121104,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T04:59:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n去邊間小屋訓？</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n原本想去高㙇小屋嘅，但去到覺得間屋好臭同有d陰森，所以臨時轉plan 去新高塚。<br />\n其實要行遠好多，但個段路因為少好多人行，所以沿路見倒幾隻鹿同馬騮。最重要係，新高塚間屋離廁所有一段距，所以屋仔唔會有公廁味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbtw, 夜晚好似有小動物出沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmo